<HEADLINE>
<P>
BASEBALL / DAILY REPORT; ANGELS; LACHEMANN HEARS FROM RODGERS, PORT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ELLIOTT TEAFORD 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 On the day after his first victory as the Angels' new manager, Marcel 
Lachemann received a congratulatory phone call from Buck Rodgers. Former Angel 
general manager Mike Port also called to offer best wishes. 
</P>
<P>
 Lachemann said his conversation with Rodgers did not involve advice on 
individual players. 
</P>
<P>
