<P>
 Children are being invited today to a free preview of Circus Vargas at the 
Children's Museum at La Habra. 
</P>
<P>
 Circus performers will present daring stunts and comedic acts at 11 a.m. as a 
pre-show for the circus, which comes to town next week. 
</P>
