 St. Bonaventure 3, Mission Prep 2 -- St. Bonaventure turned two key double 
plays early in the game to stop Mission Prep scoring threats, then rallied to 
win. Danny Harrison tripled home Jake Brown in the fifth inning as St 
Bonaventure scored three runs to take the lead. 
</P>
<P>
 Paraclete 9, Beaumont 8 -- Dennis Winchell had four hits, including the 
game-winning double in the bottom of the seventh, to lead the Spirits (12-11). 
Winchell had three doubles and a homer. DIVISION VI 
